function scaledEnemyStats(profile,tier){const scaled={};for(const key of ["health","speed","armor","evasion"]){const raw=profile?.stats?.[key],value=Logic.scaleTierFormula(raw,tier);scaled[key]=value===null?0:value}return scaled}
function availableSceneTemplates(){return TECH_SCENE_TEMPLATES.filter(template=>(S.techniques[template.tech]||0)>=template.level).concat(GIFT_SCENE_TEMPLATES.filter(template=>hasGift(template.gift)))}
